Name: Germany Berlin Bundesbank Discount Rate
Periodicity:
Monthly From Jan 1854 To Jan 1870
Weekly From Jan 1870 To Dec 1875
Daily From Jan 1876 To Jan 1908
Weekly From Jan 1908 To Jun 1914
Monthly From Jul 1914 To May 1932
Daily From May 1932 To Dec 2005
Metadata:
Sources: Hunt's Merchants Magazine (1854-1860), The Economist (1867-1875), Deutsche Bundesbank, Monthly Report (1875-)
Notes: Data are for the beginning of the month from 1867 to October 1873 and refer to Berlin. After that, data are for the end of the month at the Bundesbank.
